    • Method Detail

      • getContextHints

        @NotNull
Collection<String> getContextHints()
        Used to specify collection of editor context hints this instance is applicable to. Empty collection indicates default instance (applicable in any context). Instance is applicable in particular context only if all specified context hints are available in this context.

        When choosing an instance, the instance having the maximum number of context hints specified will be used.

        Returns:
        collection of context hints, possibly empty, never null
